## Assumptions

- Churn is defined as no activity in the following month.
- Revenue equals completed visits only.
- SMS campaign cost is assumed at 0.2 PLN per message so propose send 3 message for one client.
- Recovery rate is simulated and not based on historical data.

## Limitations

- Dataset is synthetically generated and may not reflect real patient behavior.
- No patient satisfaction or marketing data available.
- Churn definition may overestimate churn for long treatment cycles.
- ROI does not include operational costs beyond SMS campaign.
